name: State Street Gang
tagline: Low on my list of things...
body:
###Holding...

Thanks to relying on some mysql database host, I done lost everything.  It was mostly out of date, but there you go.

I'm throwing this up on github pages until I get around to doing something with it.

If you were looking for content once hosted here, you can find me on Stack Overflow. Go seek help there.

I'm @live if you want to email me.

Good luck!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
